item.title: Can someone please code for me?
item.dc:creator: @Nastay Nastay
item.description:
@Nastay wrote:

Your not allowed to be asking for others to code for you. Get up on your own read tutorials and learn, you won’t make it anywhere is private servers if others are coding your servers, I understand that if you code a server and you need help with something then you think its fine to ask but Moparscape doesn’t allow people posting asking for coders. Sorry.
